title: Breakdance Completely Street (Click2Dance)
description:
Breakdance: Completely Street - Instructional DVD (Click 2 Dance)

Learn over 25 of the industry's most popular breakdance moves! Choreographer Scotty Nguyen breaks down each lesson in a simple, yet detailed way to ensure that any student will learn something new. Regardless of your skill level, Breakdance: Completely Street offers you an inspiring and challenging experience.

Bonus Features: Sick-Step Battle and a Shane Sparks interview.

Video: 60 mins. (2007)
